News.headline: FA Youth Cup Dagenham and Redbridge v Cheshunt
News.page_title: FA Youth Cup Dagenham and Redbridge v Cheshunt
News.URL_keywords: FA Youth Cup Dagenham and Redbridge v Cheshunt
News.short_description: The Daggers Academy are playing at home in the 2nd Qualifying Round of the FA Youth Cup.
News.description:
The game will be played at the Chigwell Construction Stadium on Thursday 6th October for a 7:30pm kick-off.

Come down and support our Academy with ticket prices starting at just £1!

Ticket Prices:
Adults: £4
Concessions/Juniors: £1
